configuration file &lt;code&gt;configuration-client.properties&lt;/code&gt; (in a Git repository):

    configuration.value=Old

**Client**

Client (Spring Boot app) reads configuration from the configuration server by using [@RefreshScope][3] annotation:

&lt;!-- language: lang-java --&gt;

    @Component
    @RefreshScope
    public class Foo {
    
        @Value(&quot;${configuration.value}&quot;)
        private String value;

        ....
    }

bootstrap.yml:

    spring:
      application:
        name: configuration-client
      cloud:
